Tab stops enabled. All controls have tab stops.;
{tabstops}
{tab=x1}
{pane=One}
First Name:|[fname];
Last Name:|[lname];
<OK> <%B=T;O=Owner Draw Button%tb>
{pane=Two}
{endtab};

{lf};
Tab stops disabled. No controls in this section have tab stops.;
{notabstops}
{tab=x2}
{pane=One}
